PT PLN (Persero) — RUPTL 2025–2034
-----------------------------------
Substation lists, capacity figures, and aggregate generator statistics
in this product are derived from the Indonesia Electric Power Supply
Business Plan 2025–2034 (RUPTL PT PLN 2025–2034), a public regulatory
document authorized by:
  Decree of the Minister of Energy and Mineral Resources of the
  Republic of Indonesia, No. 188.K/TL.03/MEM.L/2025 (26 May 2025).

The original PDF document is publicly available from PLN. This
repository contains derived/aggregated information for educational
purposes; the original PDF is NOT redistributed here. See
data/raw/sources/README.md for the source URL.


Statistik PLN 2024 & 2025, Annual Report PLN 2024
--------------------------------------------------
Validation references for aggregate data are derived from publications
by PT PLN (Persero). These are publicly available corporate reports.


Handbook of Energy and Economic Statistics of Indonesia (HEESI) 2024
---------------------------------------------------------------------
Validation references are derived from a publication of the Ministry
of Energy and Mineral Resources of the Republic of Indonesia (ESDM).


